data.description: $10,000 Carpet and paint allowance. Desirable southwest location. This 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home features living room with three-way fireplace. Kitchen with breakfast bar and all appliances. Spacious dining area with sliding glass doors leading to sparkling pool, covered patio, built-in, barbecue and shed. Astroturf with low maintenance landscaping. Cul-de-sac location with spacious driveway can park multiple cars. Tankless water heater, security, lights, and refrigerator in garage included. the perfect place to call home.
